>> source: Adapted from https://denstea.com/pages/brewing
>> time required: 10 minutes
>> servings: 1

Bring water to a boil.

Measure @sencha{2*%g}

Pour @water{200*%g} into first #mug and second mug.

Throw out water in brewing mug.

Put water from second mug into the brewing mug with sencha basket. Brew for ~{1.5%minutes}.

Use for 2-3 steepings
